<script src="~/Scripts/main.js"></script>
<div class="jumbotron">
    <h1>Arduino IoT LED Cube Animations</h1>
    <p class="lead">This Website is the interface for controlling my Arduino controlled LED Cube. You can make it play an animation by pressing a button below. Give it a try!</p>
    <p><a href="https://www.github.com/vjeeva" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">See GitHub &raquo;</a></p>
</div>
<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h2>RailGun Mode</h2>
        <p>Multiple beams of light pass through the cube in a fast succession. Click it to try!</p>
        <p ><a class="btn btn-default" onclick="railGun()">Play RailGun Mode &raquo;</a></p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h2>Corner Cube Mode</h2>
        <p>Cubes grow from each corner of the cube going clockwise. Click to see it go!</p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-default" onclick="cornerCube()">Play Corner Cube Mode &raquo;</a></p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h2>Rising X Mode</h2>
        <p>An X in the cube and it rises up and down growing after each rise, and resetting after a cycle. Click to see it rise!</p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-default" onclick="risingX()">Play Corner Cube Mode &raquo;</a></p>
    </div>
</div>
